Chopped - Season 17, Episode 13




Celebrity Holiday Bash

Four stars (Antonio Sabato, Jr., Dawn Wells, Anthony Anderson and Teri Hatcher) who love to cook compete in the Chopped Kitchen for a favorite charity. The party begins with sparkling cider and doughnuts in the first basket. Wagyu steaks are served up for the entree round. And the final moments of the competition are filled with drama and suspense as the competitors rush to get their plum pudding desserts plated.




Original Air Date: 03-Dec-2013
